_super_7.htm|title=SJ Super 7|website=www.somethingjewish.co.uk}}</ref> publisher, Chairman of the ''[[Daily Express]]'' Group\n* [[Andr\u00e9 Deutsch]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2000/apr/12/news.obituaries|title=Andr\u00e9 Deutsch|first=John|last=Calder|date=12 April 2000|website=the Guardian}}</ref> publisher\n* [[Jonathan Freedland]],<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thejc.com/culture/books/freedland-thriller-1.440666|title=Freedland on Freedland|last=Freedland|first=Michael|date=29 June 2019|accessdate=27 July 2019|work=Jewish Chronicle}}</ref> journalist and author\n* [[Hadley Freeman]],<ref>{{cite news |last=Freeman |first=Hadley|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2012/nov/06/sick-of-us-news|title=Sick of US news? Don't worry: there are lots of other things to discuss |work=The Guardian|date=6 November 2012  |access-date=29 May 2018}}</ref> journalist\n* [[Tanya Gold]],<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2015/dec/05/happy-chrismukah-christian-jewish-family-festive-season-tanya-gold|title=Happy Chrismukah: our season of festive compromise|last=Gold|first=Tanya|date=5 December 2015|accessdate=9 March 2020|work=The Guardian}}</ref> journalist\n* [[Lew Grade]],<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.space1999.net/~catacombs/main/crguide/vcp.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2012-01-04 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120805134428/http://www.space1999.net/~catacombs/main/crguide/vcp.html |archivedate=5 August 2012 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> founder of [[Associated TeleVision|ATV]]\n* [[Michael Grade]],<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.itvplc.com/itv/news/releases/pr2006/2006-11-28/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2007-01-26 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070125182615/http://www.itvplc.com/itv/news/releases/pr2006/2006-11-28/ |archivedate=25 January 2007 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> Chairman of [[the BBC]] from 2004 to 2006 and executive chairman of [[ITV plc]] from 2007 to 